snippet.title: Old Love Songs by Zothiemind
snippet.description: Some people will argue that only women can write excellent love songs, however Zothiemind has demonstrated that men can write love songs that are even better than those written by women. Love songs are particularly appealing to young people because Zothiemind, who has collaborated with some of the best up-and-coming artists, has written them in a way that speaks to both coming of age and the formation of our identities. Songs are there for us when we're going through tough circumstances because they provide us with feelings and emotions to aspire to.
